&lt;p class=&quot;skrollable skrollable-between&quot; data-start=&quot;243&quot; data-end=&quot;441&quot;&gt;Are you looking for a meaningful career opportunity in the medical field? At&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong class=&quot;skrollable skrollable-between&quot; data-start=&quot;320&quot; data-end=&quot;355&quot;&gt;Urgent Care for Children (UC4C)&lt;/strong&gt;, we are always looking for passionate and dedicated professionals to join our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;skrollable skrollable-between&quot; data-start=&quot;443&quot; data-end=&quot;728&quot;&gt;Our clinics are staffed with pediatric-trained medical providers and compassionate support staff who work together to deliver exceptional after-hours care for children. We are proud to provide a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong class=&quot;skrollable skrollable-between&quot; data-start=&quot;638&quot; data-end=&quot;679&quot;&gt;supportive, team-oriented environment&lt;/strong&gt; where both patients and employees feel valued.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
