&lt;p data-start=&quot;397&quot; data-end=&quot;688&quot;&gt;We are seeking &lt;strong&gt;Pediatrician&lt;/strong&gt; to join our compassionate team at our Huntsville or Madison, AL clinic. This role is ideal for motivated clinicians who thrive in fast-paced settings, love working with kids, and want to make a meaningful impact in pediatric care, with both &lt;strong&gt;Full-Time and PRN &lt;/strong&gt;opportunities available.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
